sp.p:
                     Faustus, we are come in Person to shew thee Passtime;
sit down, and thou shalt behold the Seven Deadly
Sins in their own proper Shapes and Likeness.

And has the Doctor but one Leg then? That's Rare.
But come, this is his House, let's in and see for our Mony;
look you, we'll pay as we come back.
